  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Elliot's Show Time, you take control of Elliot Taylor, a talented guitarist performing a show with his magical guitar. But during the performance, something unexpected happens, and the rhythm of the show gets disrupted. With 10 original tracks, the game challenges your rhythm skills as you help Elliot keep the show going on stage and overcome unforeseen obstacles.</p>",
